lifter
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a shearing comb attachment that prevents a sheep being shorn too close its skin (affording protection to sheep from exposure).
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
